import React from 'react'
import { Switch, Route } from 'react-router-dom'
import Analysis from './Analysis'




var post =false;
const MainRoutes = () => (
 
  <main>
    <Switch>
      <Route exact path='/' 
    render={(props) => <Analysis {...props} post={false} />}/>
    </Switch>
    
  </main>
)

export default MainRoutes
